  ● Manual `strings.ReplaceAll`
   ╭─[test.lis:6:11]
 5 │   let s = "hello world"
 6 │   let _ = mystr.Replace(s, "o", "0", -1)
   ·           ───────────────┬──────────────
   ·                          ╰── can use `strings.ReplaceAll`
 7 │ }
   ╰────
  help: `mystr.Replace(s, "o", "0", -1)` replaces every occurrence. Use `mystr.ReplaceAll(s, "o", "0")` · code: [lint.manual_replace_all]
